    <item>
      <title>Save The Castle</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/01/22/save-castle/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Jan 2012 22:34:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/01/22/save-castle/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sad news has reached us. Our beloved Castle has just learned that a planning application has been sent to the council to
knock it down and build apartments and a parking lot!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Go to &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.wandsworth.gov.uk/info/1023/planning_advice_and_guidance/364/find_a_planning_application&#34;&gt;wandsworth.gov.uk find a planning
application&lt;/a&gt; and
search for application number 2012/0229 to protest and keep track of the application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    &lt;img 
      
      srcset=&#39;
      
