    <item>
      <title>Afternoon tea and ice skating</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/01/07/afternoon-tea-and-ice-skating/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Jan 2012 19:08:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/01/07/afternoon-tea-and-ice-skating/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Today we went to have afternoon tea at the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.washington-mayfair.co.uk/&#34;&gt;Washington Mayfair Hotel&lt;/a&gt;. Nice place
and lovely atmosphere but I don&amp;rsquo;t think I&amp;rsquo;d come here again. Staff are friendly enough and at £25 a head for afternoon
tea including a cocktail, the price isn&amp;rsquo;t bad. What spoiled it is the poor quality of the food and drinks. Tasted like
it was pre packed and not made up fresh.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    &lt;img 
      
      srcset=&#39;
      
      
      
      &#39;
